<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    @{
        ViewBag.title = "Challenges - Building Resilience";
    }

    <!-- Favicon -->
    @*<link rel="shortcut icon" href="assets/img/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">*@

    <!-- Font awesome -->
    <link href="~/Content/all.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link href="~/Content/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Slick slider -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="~/Content/slick.css">
    <!-- Fancybox slider -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/jquery.fancybox.css" type="text/css" media="screen" />
    <!-- Theme color -->
    <link id="switcher" href="~/Content/default-theme.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Main style sheet -->
    <link href="~/Content/style.css" rel="stylesheet">


    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:400,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:400,400italic,300,300italic,500,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>


    <!-- HTML5 shim and Respond.js for IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries -->
    <!-- WARNING: Respond.js doesn't work if you view the page via file:// -->
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/html5shiv/3.7.2/html5shiv.min.js"></script>
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/respond/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->

</head>
<body>
    <a class="scrollToTop" href="#">
        <i class="fa fa-angle-up"></i>
    </a>

    <!-- Page breadcrumb -->
    <section id="mu-page-breadcrumb">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <div class="mu-page-breadcrumb-area">
                        <h2>Challenges</h2>
                        <ol class="breadcrumb">
                            <li>@Html.ActionLink("Home", "Index", "Home")</li>
                            <li class="active">@Html.ActionLink("Challenges", "Index", "Challenges")</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- End breadcrumb -->

    <section id="mu-course-content">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <div class="mu-latest-course-single">
                        <div class="mu-latest-course-single-content">
                            <h2>What are some of the changes young kids face?</h2>
                            <p>Young children face a lot of challenges while growing up today. A lot of these issues affect the child's overall growth and development.</p>
                            <p>Numerous studies have shown that children who grow up with such challenges in their life often end up having behavioural issues when they grow up or end up on the wrong side of the law.</p>
                            <p>Some of the common challenges children face are listed below. You can click on them to read more.</p>
                            <h6>@Html.ActionLink("Bullying", "Bullying", "Challenges")</h6>
                            <h6>@Html.ActionLink("Child Abuse", "Abuse", "Challenges")</h6>
                            <h6>@Html.ActionLink("Family Violence", "Violence", "Challenges")</h6>
                            <p>Take a look at the proportion of children that have a high level of family stress: </p>
                            <div>
                                <a href="https://plot.ly/~aram0010/20/?share_key=CV6xk1YPmeGaxXH2pXu3cq" target="_blank" title="Family stress" style="display: block; text-align: center;"><img src="https://plot.ly/~aram0010/20.png?share_key=CV6xk1YPmeGaxXH2pXu3cq" alt="Family stress" style="max-width: 100%;width: 600px;" width="600" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://plot.ly/404.png';" /></a>
                                <script data-plotly="aram0010:20" sharekey-plotly="CV6xk1YPmeGaxXH2pXu3cq&autosize=true&modebar=false&link=false" src="https://plot.ly/embed.js" async></script>
                            </div>
                            <p>Here we see the proportion of children that deal with emotional or behavior difficulties: </p>
                            <div>
                                <a href="https://plot.ly/~aram0010/16/?share_key=7vocCcJ67B8KScmOA3M0Lf" target="_blank" title="Behaviour Dif." style="display: block; text-align: center;"><img src="https://plot.ly/~aram0010/16.png?share_key=7vocCcJ67B8KScmOA3M0Lf" alt="Behaviour Dif." style="max-width: 100%;width: 600px;" width="600" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://plot.ly/404.png';" /></a>
                                <script data-plotly="aram0010:16" sharekey-plotly="7vocCcJ67B8KScmOA3M0Lf&autosize=true&modebar=false&link=false" src="https://plot.ly/embed.js" async></script>
                            </div>
                            <p>School is no longer a safe learning space efor most students. Here we see the percentage of children that say that school is a safe learning space: </p>
                            <div>
                                <a href="https://plot.ly/~aram0010/28/?share_key=qQRRrKRjduXR85F6udjOay" target="_blank" title="Believing School safe" style="display: block; text-align: center;"><img src="https://plot.ly/~aram0010/28.png?share_key=qQRRrKRjduXR85F6udjOay" alt="Believing School safe" style="max-width: 100%;width: 600px;" width="600" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://plot.ly/404.png';" /></a>
                                <script data-plotly="aram0010:28" sharekey-plotly="qQRRrKRjduXR85F6udjOay&autosize=true&modebar=false&link=false" src="https://plot.ly/embed.js" async></script>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- jQuery library -->
    <script src="~/Scripts/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Include all compiled plugins (below), or include individual files as needed -->
    <script src="~/Scripts/bootstrap.js"></script>
    <!-- Slick slider -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="~/Scripts/slick.js"></script>
    <!-- Counter -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="~/Scripts/waypoints.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="~/Scripts/jquery.counterup.js"></script>
    <!-- Mixit slider -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="~/Scripts/jquery.mixitup.js"></script>
    <!-- Add fancyBox -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="~/Scripts/jquery.fancybox.pack.js"></script>


    <!-- Custom js -->
    <script src="~/Scripts/custom.js"></script>
</body>
</html>